[{"id":6489,"date":"2026-03-25T06:34:30","link":"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/vysprava-vytluku-novou-mikrovlnou-technologii-na-silnici-na-silnici-ii-297-v-useku-svoboda-nad-upou-cerny-dul-a-ii-296-mezi-svobodou-nad-upou-a-mladymi-buky\/","title":{"rendered":"V\u00fdsprava v\u00fdtluk\u016f novou mikrovlnou technologi\u00ed na silnici na silnici II\/297 v\u00a0\u00faseku Svoboda nad \u00dapou \u2013 \u010cern\u00fd D\u016fl a II\/296 mezi Svobodou nad \u00dapou a Mlad\u00fdmi Buky"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>24.3.2026 v\u00a0podve\u010der a v\u00a0no\u010dn\u00edch hodin\u00e1ch byla na silnici II\/297 v\u00a0\u00faseku Svoboda nad \u00dapou \u2013 \u010cern\u00fd D\u016fl a II\/296 mezi Svobodou nad \u00dapou a Mlad\u00fdmi Buky provedena v\u00fdsprava v\u00fdtluk\u016f pomoc\u00ed nov\u00e9 mikrovlnn\u00e9 technologie FUTTEC\u00ae.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Principem patentu firmy FUTTEC a.s. je mikrovlnn\u00e9 z\u00e1\u0159en\u00ed, kter\u00e9 dok\u00e1\u017ee \u0161etrn\u011b oh\u0159\u00e1t sm\u011bs asfaltu a&nbsp;kameniva na kontrolovanou teplotu 120 a\u017e 160\u202f\u00b0C. Asfaltov\u00e9 pojivo na hranici neporu\u0161en\u00e9 vozovky a\u202fv\u00fdtluku tak zm\u011bkne, ale nepo\u0161kod\u00ed se.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pak se do v\u00fdtluku p\u0159id\u00e1 d\u00e1vkovan\u00e1 asfaltov\u00e1 sm\u011bs odpov\u00eddaj\u00edc\u00ed po\u0161kozen\u00e9 \u010d\u00e1sti silnice, kter\u00e1 je tak\u00e9 oh\u0159\u00e1t\u00e1 pomoc\u00ed mikrovln, a&nbsp;v\u0161e se zhutn\u00ed. V\u00fdsledkem je dokonal\u00e1 bezesp\u00e1r\u00e1 a&nbsp;trvanliv\u00e1 oprava v\u00fdtluku, kter\u00e1 uvede vozovku do p\u016fvodn\u00edho stavu.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u00dadr\u017ebu mikrovlnnou technologi\u00ed lze prov\u00e1d\u011bt na vozovk\u00e1ch s&nbsp;r\u016fzn\u00fdm typem asfaltov\u00e9ho povrchu, st\u00e1\u0159\u00edm, sklonem i&nbsp;m\u00edrou po\u0161kozen\u00ed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mikrovlnn\u00e1 technologie jako jedin\u00e1 dok\u00e1\u017ee zachovat vlastnosti p\u016fvodn\u00ed vozovky: tedy zacelit v\u00fdtluk bez zm\u011bny jej\u00edch p\u016fvodn\u00edch parametr\u016f, p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm \u00fanosnosti a&nbsp;protismykov\u00fdch vlastnost\u00ed. \u017divotnost vozovky nav\u00edc prodlu\u017euje t\u00edm, \u017ee neroz\u0161i\u0159uje opravovanou plochu fr\u00e9zov\u00e1n\u00edm ani bour\u00e1n\u00edm, nedod\u00e1v\u00e1 do n\u00ed recyklovan\u00fd materi\u00e1l s&nbsp;jinou zrnitost\u00ed a&nbsp;nevznikaj\u00ed p\u0159i&nbsp;n\u00ed \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 sp\u00e1ry.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Oprava v\u00fdtluku je celkem rychl\u00e1, trv\u00e1 30 minut a\u017e 1 hodinu.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Inovativn\u00ed mikrovlnn\u00fd syst\u00e9m FUTTEC\u00ae, kter\u00fd byl vyvinut ve spolupr\u00e1ci s\u00a0\u00dastavem chemick\u00fdch proces\u016f Akademie v\u011bd \u010cR a\u00a0s\u00a0VUT v\u00a0Brn\u011b, m\u00e1 \u010desk\u00fd patent a\u00a0ji\u017e bylo po\u017e\u00e1d\u00e1no tak\u00e9 o\u00a0patenty v\u00a0EU a\u00a0dal\u0161\u00edch sedmi zem\u00edch cel\u00e9ho sv\u011bta od USA a\u017e po\u00a0Japonsko.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"6491\"  src=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/1-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.0-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6491\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/1-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.0-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/1-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.0-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/1-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.0-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/1-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.0-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/1-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.0.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy