MT-II-297-23.3.2026.1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" data-id=\"6496\"  src=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/8-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.13-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6496\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/8-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.13-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/8-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.13-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/8-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.13-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/8-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.13-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/8-Vyspravy-MT-II-297-23.3.2026.13.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>24.3.2026 v\u00a0podve\u010der a v\u00a0no\u010dn\u00edch hodin\u00e1ch byla na silnici II\/297 v\u00a0\u00faseku Svoboda nad \u00dapou \u2013 \u010cern\u00fd D\u016fl a II\/296 mezi Svobodou nad \u00dapou a Mlad\u00fdmi Buky provedena v\u00fdsprava v\u00fdtluk\u016f pomoc\u00ed nov\u00e9 mikrovlnn\u00e9 technologie FUTTEC\u00ae. Principem patentu firmy FUTTEC a.s. je mikrovlnn\u00e9 z\u00e1\u0159en\u00ed, kter\u00e9 dok\u00e1\u017ee \u0161etrn\u011b oh\u0159\u00e1t sm\u011bs asfaltu a&nbsp;kameniva na kontrolovanou teplotu 120 a\u017e 160\u202f\u00b0C. Asfaltov\u00e9 &hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false}},{"id":6277,"date":"2025-11-19T11:05:07","link":"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/stavba-silnice-ii-327-zabedov-novy-bydzov\/","title":{"rendered":"Stavba silnice II\/327 Z\u00e1b\u011bdov \u2013 Nov\u00fd Byd\u017eov"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Dnes v Nov\u00e9m Byd\u017eov\u011b prob\u011bhlo slavnostn\u00ed ukon\u010den\u00ed stavby silnice II\/327 Z\u00e1b\u011bdov \u2013 Nov\u00fd Byd\u017eov. Akce se z\u00fa\u010dastnili p\u0159edstaviteli Kr\u00e1lov\u00e9hradeck\u00e9ho kraje, starost Nov\u00e9ho Byd\u017eova a z\u00e1stupce zhotovitele CH&amp;T Pardubice. Silnice II\/327 m\u00e1 region\u00e1ln\u00ed v\u00fdznam, propojuje v\u00fdznamn\u00e1 m\u011bsta regionu Chlumec nad Cidlinou a Nov\u00fd Byd\u017eov. P\u0159edm\u011btem stavby byla oprava silnice II\/327 ze Z\u00e1b\u011bdova do Nov\u00e9ho Byd\u017eova o celkov\u00e9 d\u00e9lce 2,575 km. Sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed byla i rekonstrukce mostu ev. \u010d. 327-018, roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed komunikace pro odbo\u010dovac\u00ed pruhy a \u00fapravy autobusov\u00fdch z\u00e1liv\u016f. Soub\u011b\u017en\u011b s rekonstrukc\u00ed silnice II\/327 byla prov\u00e1d\u011bna tak\u00e9 v\u00fdstavba chodn\u00edk\u016f pro p\u011b\u0161\u00ed a m\u00edsty i sm\u00ed\u0161en\u00e9 stezky pro p\u011b\u0161\u00ed a cyklisty jej\u00edm\u017e investorem je m\u011bsto Nov\u00fd Byd\u017eov.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"626\" data-id=\"6278\"  src=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1-1024x626.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6278\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1-1024x626.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1-300x183.jpg 300w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1-768x470.jpg 768w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1-600x367.jpg 600w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/1.jpg 1408w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" data-id=\"6284\"  src=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/2-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6284\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/uskhk