figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Dnes v Nov\u00e9m Byd\u017eov\u011b prob\u011bhlo slavnostn\u00ed ukon\u010den\u00ed stavby silnice II\/327 Z\u00e1b\u011bdov \u2013 Nov\u00fd Byd\u017eov. Akce se z\u00fa\u010dastnili p\u0159edstaviteli Kr\u00e1lov\u00e9hradeck\u00e9ho kraje, starost Nov\u00e9ho Byd\u017eova a z\u00e1stupce zhotovitele CH&amp;T Pardubice. Silnice II\/327 m\u00e1 region\u00e1ln\u00ed v\u00fdznam, propojuje v\u00fdznamn\u00e1 m\u011bsta regionu Chlumec nad Cidlinou a Nov\u00fd Byd\u017eov. P\u0159edm\u011btem stavby byla oprava silnice II\/327 ze Z\u00e1b\u011bdova do Nov\u00e9ho Byd\u017eova o &hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false}},{"id":5812,"date":"2025-05-15T06:12:30","link":"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/rekonstrukce-silnice-iii-28038-sekerice-hlusicky\/","title":{"rendered":"Rekonstrukce silnice III\/28038 Seke\u0159ice &#8211; Hlu\u0161i\u010dky"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>V okrese Ji\u010d\u00edn je v pln\u00e9m proudu oprava silnice III\/28038 Seke\u0159ice &#8211; Hlu\u0161i\u010dky. Silnice vykazovala mno\u017estv\u00ed nerovnost\u00ed a konstruk\u010dn\u00edch poruch, proto bude sou\u010dasn\u00e1 konstruk\u010dn\u00ed vrstva vyfr\u00e9zov\u00e1na a bude realizov\u00e1na pokl\u00e1dka podkladn\u00ed a obrusn\u00e9 asfaltobetonov\u00e9 vrstvy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" data-id=\"5816\"  src=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5816\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/uskhk.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/1-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/usk